50:39.083 --> 50:40.208
Ayah?

50:43.333 --> 50:44.625
Istana…

50:47.541 --> 50:48.500
Raja…

50:51.416 --> 50:52.291
Rumah…

50:55.625 --> 50:56.458
Anakku…

50:59.333 --> 51:00.166
Percayalah…

51:22.541 --> 51:23.375
Ayah?

51:26.708 --> 51:27.583
Ayah?

51:29.333 --> 51:30.208
